* Hobbies
I spend a good deal of time on an assortment of hobbies, often without the consent of the more productive part of my brain.
** Music
From what I can recall, most of my life has been centered around music. I have many valuable memories from having made music such a huge part of my life during high school and the start of college. Someday I will include a link here for more information on my music experience for anyone who might be interested. Though I am a drummer by training, I've learned to play many popular songs on the piano and guitar which I might list here also someday. I do not really listen to music as much as I once did, but if I do it tends to be of more ambient or unfamiliar styles. Most songs seem to get old quickly for me, so I am always looking for a new genre. 

